</taxonomicName>
(represented by the synonym 
<taxonomicName id="4C314D724103FF85FB34546AFA5F3A05" authorityName="Fowler" authorityYear="1936" box="[1157,1428,1028,1049]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Poeciliidae" genus="Aplocheilichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="13" pageNumber="57" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="vanderbilti">
<emphasis id="B945EAE34103FF85FB34546AFA5F3A05" box="[1157,1428,1028,1049]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="57">Aplocheilichthys vanderbilti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
)
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8E36F14103FF85FF26544FFA573A4F" blockId="13.[151,1437,969,1108]" pageId="13" pageNumber="57">
<keyLead id="30C095C44103FF85FF26544FFA573A4F" pageId="13" pageNumber="57">
- Body size smaller than 
<quantity id="4CC99B144103FF85FE7B544FFDC53A2A" box="[458,526,1057,1078]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="57" unit="mm" value="30.0">30 mm</quantity>
SL; median fins without striped pattern of dark bands; number of scales in mid-longitudinal series 24-27......................................................................................... 2
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="30C52E544103FF85FF265417FA573AB7" pageId="13" pageNumber="57">
